Let's begin!

27
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:16,100
You're done! Congratulations!

28
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:23,220
By the way, the /ɑ/ sound is most often written as the letter “o.”

29
00:04:24,140 --> 00:04:26,480
More on the spelling:

30
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:34,080
the letter “o” stands for the /ɑ/ sound, as in the word “got,” in 87% of cases.

31
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:40,320
The remaining 13% belong to the letter “a,” as in the word “want.”

32
00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:49,780
Sometimes, this sound is written by a combination of the letters “al,” as in the word “calm.”

33
